    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/c6fdf111cd5e1c2c705f595856113cf8.avif?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被抛入陌生的竞技场，被数百只怪物包围，你只有一个任务——坚持活过五秒钟。你不是传说中的英雄，而是一次失败的军事实验产物。幸运的是，你拥有比史诗血统更强大的东西——一个荒诞的武器库，以及彻底释放混乱的自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Blast Head》是一款 <i>Roguelite</i> 风格的 <i>Bullet Heaven</i> 游戏，屏幕会瞬间变成由弹幕、爆炸和越来越离奇的武器组成的彩色万花筒。在这里，每一局都是一次实验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/66fa103eb0c35885a3253f07b1dd0134.webp?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/d7f07ab8799525ca466d7c3e3e1732a5.avif?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/82594516a974e7c34a131d6a6b709f13.poster.avif?t=1769633195\" width=608 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/82594516a974e7c34a131d6a6b709f13.webm?t=1769633195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/82594516a974e7c34a131d6a6b709f13.mp4?t=1769633195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过10种独特武器——每种武器都拥有自己的庞大技能树，包含10–15个可解锁的能力。这不仅仅是提升数值，而是决定你的游戏风格。你可以把一把普通的弹弓变成毁灭性的屠杀工具，或者打造一个将敌人拖入混乱漩涡的组合。武器可以融合、强化、自由实验，从而发现出乎意料的协同效果，在瞬间清空整个屏幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/4dcc612d88324be2ead339e95dc21e4c.avif?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想让游戏自动进行？开启自动射击，专注于闪避。想要冒险？提升敌人密度，换来更丰厚的奖励。或者你希望强制触发特殊事件？符文可以改变游戏的基本规则——它们让每一局都与众不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/676a2dfad13661c7d562663406f5decf.avif?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里没有无聊可言。弹弓、人字拖、酸液罐、混沌球甚至是爱的弓箭——武器越荒诞，摧毁怪物大军时的快感就越强。每件武器都有独特的个性和成长，当你开始将它们组合起来……就是纯粹的毁灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/848d46d8436081163e6427179677b176.avif?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不需要耗掉整晚——每局仅需10–30分钟，但紧张感一刻也不会放松。纯粹的动作体验，屏幕会迅速变成弹幕、特效与敌人的万花筒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/78148036d25c91c8e2a1704118b88f22.avif?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次尝试都是一个新故事。随机事件、多样的符文以及数十种构筑方式，确保没有两局是完全相同的。你的角色不仅仅是一个英雄——而是疯狂的视听化身，会与你一同成长与变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/df5262a9f1eb450c98b4ea3c68a538c1.avif?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一开始，你面对的只是一些可以轻松粉碎的小虫子。但随着时间推移，情况会越来越糟。更庞大的敌人浪潮、更狂暴的对手，以及需要创造力和一丝绝望才能战胜的Boss。在这里，每一个失误都要付出生命代价，而每一次胜利都会加倍甘甜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/66fa103eb0c35885a3253f07b1dd0134.webp?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Blast Head》是一款将混乱转化为毁灭艺术的游戏，每一件武器、每一局游戏都能带来全新的屠杀方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054260/extras/66fa103eb0c35885a3253f07b1dd0134.webp?t=1769633195\" width=609 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将 <strong>Blast Head</strong> 添加到你的 Steam 愿望单，准备迎接一场彻底荒诞的芭蕾吧！</p>",
